org.hkijena.jipipe.api.data

Interface JIPipeSlotConfiguration

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    JIPipeMutableSlotConfiguration
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JIPipeDefaultMutableSlotConfiguration, JIPipeIOSlotConfiguration

    public interface JIPipeSlotConfiguration
    A slot configuration determines which slots an JIPipeGraphNode should have. The algorithm then instantiates JIPipeDataSlot instances to match the configuration. This is required to allow multiple algorithms to share their slots.
